				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The game probably checks PlayerStatus when a box is hit to know whether a mushroom or a flower must show up. Then, both the mushroom and the flower probably just increment PlayerStatus when Mario picks them up. So yeah, picking up a mushroom while Super Mario will turn him into Fire Mario.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

