					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">JohnJohn wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">How do I do this during gameplay?</div>
<br />Open the game in FCEUXD. Hit the mushroom box and once the mushroom is out and moving pause the game. Open the hex editor (Tools -&gt; Hex Editor), scroll down until you see memory locations $0754 and $0756. Change $0754 to $00 (click the old value and type the new value) to make Mario big and $0756 to $01 to make him Super. Unpause the game and pick up the mushroom.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

